Patch Set 2: Code-Review+2

This makes sense.  As a followup, we should update docs and api-ref and add a release note.  I don't think it requires an API version bump because with property protections, it's been possible for a long time to include a "restricted" namespace specific to a particular cloud, so clients should be open to the possibility that a create-image request could be rejected due to specifying a restricted custom property.
